casebody.data:
No. 65, Original. State of Texas, Plaintiff v. State of New Mexico. 565 U.S. 809, 132 S. Ct. 81,

181 L. Ed. 2d 12,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6683. October 3, 2011.

Motion of the River Master for fees and reimbursement of *13expenses granted, and the River Master is awarded a total of $6,885.82 for the period July 1, 2010, through June 30, 2011, to be paid equally by the parties.
